  "statement": {
    "en": "Ramanujan tau function: τ(n) defined via Δ(q) = q·Π(1-q^n)^24 = Σ τ(n)q^n. Mock-mysteriously multiplicative: τ(mn) = τ(m)τ(n) for (m,n)=1. Proven via Hecke operators; |τ(p)| ≤ 2p^(11/2) (Deligne 1974, Weil conjectures).",
    "ja": null,
    "latex": "\\Delta(q) = q\\prod_{n=1}^{\\infty}(1-q^n)^{24} = \\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\tau(n)q^n",
